tags.description: Field dedicated to community leader Joe Montana, used by local youth sport organizations for baseball football and soccer sporting events. Local schools also often use the field for end of the year graduation ceremonies.
tags.name: Joe Montana Feild

tags.description: Memorial park set up in the middle of town to honor former firefighter Kevin Landau, who was killed in a tragic accident on service. Park is set up with a beautiful fountain and plaque, along with park benches and flower beds.
tags.name: Kevin Landau Memorial Park
